query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.favorite_count >= 0 AND q1.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('angular-momentum',
'bash',
'electricity',
'electrons',
'entropy',
'everyday-life',
'gauge-theory',
'jquery',
'kinematics',
'orbital-motion',
'quantum-information',
'quantum-spin',
'schroedinger-equation',
'speed-of-light',
'windows-server-2008')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('codereview',
'physics',
'serverfault')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.reputation >= 10 AND u1.reputation <= 100000 group by t1.name;
